        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1421198389" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16737407966442707905">•	Oh my! Kaylee Song has done it again-She wrote another great book AND she wrote this book so I COULDN’T go to bed until I finished it- but she is forgiven because this book had everything that I loved that made this a kick a&amp;&amp; book. Bad Boy is on the hunt and he has his sight on the prize…target…well, you get the picture. This is one fantastic story that has action, suspense, hot and passionate copulation, and big BAD MAFIA guys. Oh but there is so much more to this story…Two Mafia families at</span>
  <span id="freeText16737407966442707905" style="display:none">•	Oh my! Kaylee Song has done it again-She wrote another great book AND she wrote this book so I COULDN’T go to bed until I finished it- but she is forgiven because this book had everything that I loved that made this a kick a&amp;&amp; book. Bad Boy is on the hunt and he has his sight on the prize…target…well, you get the picture. This is one fantastic story that has action, suspense, hot and passionate copulation, and big BAD MAFIA guys. Oh but there is so much more to this story…Two Mafia families at war, two mafia kids in love (Romeo and Julia?) and so much more…<br /><br /><br />Joanna is working off her father’s debt to Grayson’s father in a bar when she sees him one night getting beat up. She just says something and that was the beginning to the end for Greyson wanted her and what he wanted he got. Joanna is hiding secrets for her family is one of their emeries in the Mob side. She took the job only so she didn’t have to her uncle. Soon she and Greyson are going out and that is when things blow sky-high. They are forced into a situation cause by her family, there is a rat and loyalties are divided. Bad things are coming. Greyson is a tough alpha male and he WANTS Jo, NEEDS Jo…what he wants, he gets. Jo on the other hand, hates being forced into situations that she didn’t ask for. She has defnately strong feelings for Greyson and their intimate moments are intense and the sex is OMG intense..As a reader, I loved the sex scenes; This story is about a couple who finds love out of a strong moment in time and while being forced by outside forces. Can their love that is brewing have a chance or will the danger from the rat strike and Jo be hurt?<br /> <br /><br /><br />I hope the author will write a follow-up book about the secondary cast of characters in the story-- Mary, Willa and Janson . They definitely need their own stories written.<br /><br />My Rating: 5.0 *****<br />***A gifted copy was provided by the author for my honest review****<br /></span>
