  <span id="freeText17951419077410999368" style="display:none">This is a BRILLIANT MUST READ<br /> <br /> wow Kaylee has got you pulled straight into the relationship between Joanne O'Brien the niece of the enemy of Greyson's, other Mob family without knowing who she is except that he wants her that one time si she's out of his system. <br /> He has to have her no matter what &amp; that's what happened when they are seen and photographed together they have to be married even though they try to fight it they can't help fall in love without actually knowing each other. There I'd do much tension and oh his if you love reading sexually appetite this is for you and it gets your heart pumping wondering if they can stay together with what their families trying to be the top ones.<br />Has Joanne lost everything when Greyson finds out she betrayed him by giving her uncle what he wanted even though it was life or death but now the morning after their wedding he pushed her out and became the monster he knew he was. Well that was until he finds out she's with his child &amp; then his brother had kidnapped her. Can Greyson save Joanne and his own life after he goes to get her???<br /><br />Story 2 RAGE<br />I adored this edge on seat story between Rage 'Cullen' and Lala 'Layla'<br /> Layla left behind her life from the MC when she was a teenager after the death of her father due to his life as president of the MC and she couldn't stay and watch the same thing happen to her brother Sean and his best mate come her boyfriend Cullen as she knew they were going to join and be big in the MC.<br />Though Layla had to go back for the funeral of the murder of Sean and then told she had to stay to keep her safe which kills both her and Cullen who is now 2nd in command, who still blames her for leaving him. Bones the current president says She stays and becomes their accountant then after getting involved with their competitors from another MC and the Irish Mob Who gets her to do some accounting work for them in exchange of them helping hunt down the be MC gang (who deals in with drugs)around town who owned up to Sean's murder and then the gun down of another of their men. After finding where one of the mobs employee's hangs out who dealt with the group's drug selling to the mob, see's 1 that was at the shooting who tells him that it was one of theirs that told them to take the blame.<br /> During their time back together again had brought them back together romantically again also after finding out who was the one killing Layla's family the men who Cullen trusts gets together without telling Layla that he's leaving and where to that she gets a visit from a old hated school friend who has been with Cullen, saying she wants to make amends but was setting her up and drugs her to take her to Bones, can Cullen, Thrash and Uncle Mick get to her BEFORE Bones does anything to her....</span>
