<span id="freeTextContainer4107994629614322397"><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1435800549i/15379513._SY540_.jpg' width='250' height='250' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><b>
  <i>He was everything I never thought I wanted, but everything I needed. At least at the moment.</i>
