        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1486497016" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1847821710467851866">BOOKS:<br/>WED TO THE BAD BOY<br/>STOLEN:A BAD BOY ROMANCE<br/><br/>AUTHOR: KAILEE SONG<br/>MAD LOVE RATING:<br/>❤️❤️❤️<br/><br/>I bought one book and to my surprise, I got two. The first book is also included in the .99 cents price, i had paid for Stolen: A Bad Boy Romance,but i also got, as a bonus from the author, the first book in the series: Wed to the Bad Boy. What an excellent bargain. I started reading and read both books back to back. HEAVEN! <br/><br/>The stories are solid y bien entretenidas, No cabe dudas que la autora sabe como los</span>
  <span id="freeText1847821710467851866" style="display:none">BOOKS:<br />WED TO THE BAD BOY<br />STOLEN:A BAD BOY ROMANCE<br /><br />AUTHOR: KAILEE SONG<br />MAD LOVE RATING:<br />❤️❤️❤️<br /><br />I bought one book and to my surprise, I got two. The first book is also included in the .99 cents price, i had paid for Stolen: A Bad Boy Romance,but i also got, as a bonus from the author, the first book in the series: Wed to the Bad Boy. What an excellent bargain. I started reading and read both books back to back. HEAVEN! <br /><br />The stories are solid y bien entretenidas, No cabe dudas que la autora sabe como los machos actúan. I enjoyed the characters and their chemistry, Si, la verdad es que tienen un temperamento bien fuerte, but mostly, I loved the way both men reacted to non-sense. However, the stories are very short, and they end abruptly. It stared promising, me llamo la atencion y no pude dejar de leerlos. As soon as I started reading, i couldn't put it down....but when you are getting the hang of the story, right at the climax....it ends....Finito, The End, se acabó. BOTH OF THEM!!!! Now, I understand why the author decided to put them together.<br /><br />So, if you'd like to take advantage of this bargain, the books are still .99 cents, i don't know until when...however, at the time of this posting that was the sale price. Asi que aprovecha y compralos, si quieres una lectura corta y entretenida, pero estan advertidos. <br /><br />AMAZON Kindle:<br />Wed to the bad boy: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://amzn.to/1Py5g74">http://amzn.to/1Py5g74</a><br />Stolen: A Bad Boy Romance: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://amzn.to/1mSwFr3">http://amzn.to/1mSwFr3</a></span>
