        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1432964678" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2379195195614587953">Definitely disappointed with how quickly the author chose to end this book. The story line itself was good and had so much potential to make an amazing novel, but unfortunately it felt as though the author ran out of time and just ended it as quickly as possible. I could have seen this story line developing much further that what it was for sure. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


