        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1458445630" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15940465709212982259">DNF - a little to over the top. I am not into mob books and this book is a good example of why. She is forced to marry him and she&apos;s like &apos;well there&apos;s nothing I can do, what my uncle wants her gets&apos; and the conversation about the marriage that he had with his mother was the last straw for me.</span>
