        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1430672568" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10034046846887217947"><i> ARC given in exchange for an honest review </i><br/><br/>HOT HOT HOT!!!! Kaylee doesn&apos;t disappoint in this book! She brings it all again and knows how to get you hooked from the beginning. The story has a good plot and it sticks till the very end. The emotions will run high in this book and the chemistry is hot &amp; steamy too. Overall a great read especially if you like mafia romance.<br/><br/>Joanna has never lived her life the way she has wanted to. When your family is in the mob and you have to depend on an Uncle, yo</span>
  <span id="freeText10034046846887217947" style="display:none"><i> ARC given in exchange for an honest review </i><br /><br />HOT HOT HOT!!!! Kaylee doesn't disappoint in this book! She brings it all again and knows how to get you hooked from the beginning. The story has a good plot and it sticks till the very end. The emotions will run high in this book and the chemistry is hot &amp; steamy too. Overall a great read especially if you like mafia romance.<br /><br />Joanna has never lived her life the way she has wanted to. When your family is in the mob and you have to depend on an Uncle, you know it's a life you don't want. Joanna works off a debt that her father has at Greyson's spot and was warned to stay away from Greyson. However she gets noticed by Greyson and there is no escaping him. One night with Greyson is what she'll do but it won't be enough.<br /><br />Greyson is the alpha mafia bad boy and he calls himself a monster. Everyone looks at him that way and he is the heir into the business. He does what is needed and gets the job done. He goes to his spot and sees Joanna - he has to have her and will stop at nothing to get her. One night is all he needs, only he was wrong. <br /><br />Joanna &amp; Greyson's journey isn't pretty and you'll face all the battles with them. Two people who are opposites from each other, come together. The emotions will play hard on you and you will feel the love form between the characters. <br /><br />Great job to the author on another great read! I highly recommend. </span>
  <a data-text-id="10034046846887217947" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
